body_html: This happened to me (with Keras) but I updated cuDNN (from 7.1 to 7.2), reinstalled tensorflow-gpu, and it worked! Whatever your case, a good starting point is always downloading the Jupyter Notebook to a .py script and running it. At least it will give you more the complete errors/warnings.
